description:
Cubitt is sports and health App with new features.
－It integrates such functions as health data recording, movement track recording and wearable device control, acting as your exclusive health steward.
－It records all data from your wearable device, allowing you to focus more on your exercise!

After connecting your wearable device to the Cubitt App, you have access to:
[Manage Health]: 
Record and manage the monitoring data on stress, sleep, and set the menstrual cycle reminder;
Set alarms, call reminders, message notifications, inactivity reminders, drinking reminders, serving as an assistant in your life;
Record your sleep data, including sleep duration, deep sleep, light sleep and rapid eye movements (REM), in order to monitor and improve your sleep quality;
Record your weight trends and set your weight goal, encouraging you to achieve the daily exercise goal;

[Record Exercise& Activities]: 
Record your exercise data sports (running, biking, swimming, rowing machine, etc.), including your movement track, HR, pace, etc.;
Record your daily walking steps, calories, medium and high-intensity exercise and other activity data, and view the complete records on a daily/weekly/monthly basis;

[Change Dial]: A rich selection of watch face themes are available in the brand-new cloud dial market, giving your device a new look every day;

[Share Achievements]: If you use Cubitt App to monitor your excercises continuously, virtual medals will be awarded when you reaches milestones. You can share your weekly exercise information for interaction with your friends.

[Data Share]: Connect to synchronize data to Apple Health (HealthKit), to achieve data movement, data and consumed calories sleep simultaneous recording to Apple Health (HealthKit)

Cubitt App supports multiple languages, and it will support more wearable devices in the future, bringing you more wonderful experiences!
You are welcome to send you feedback to: Help@cubittofficial.com
